## Complete checklist

### New page
- [ ] `PageEnum` ‚Äî new value with `[Description]`
- [ ] `NavService.cs` ‚Äî `NavItem` with `Role = nameof(PageEnum.*)`
- [ ] `.razor` file ‚Äî `@attribute [Authorize(Roles = nameof(PageEnum.*))]`

### New function
- [ ] `FunctionEnum` ‚Äî new value with `[Description]`
- [ ] `TenantDatabaseInitializer.cs ‚Üí FunctionPageMap` ‚Äî new entry
- [ ] Razor ‚Äî `<AuthorizeView Roles="@nameof(FunctionEnum.*)">` and/or `IsInRole(nameof(FunctionEnum.*))`

### New grid column
- [ ] `PageColumnEnum` ‚Äî new value with `[Description]`
- [ ] `TenantDatabaseInitializer.cs ‚Üí ColumnPageMap` ‚Äî new entry
- [ ] Razor ‚Äî `Visible="@Col(nameof(PageColumnEnum.*))"`

